ABOUT OUR PROJECT

FishEye International, a non-profit focused on countering IUU fishing, has been given access to an international finance corporation's database on fishing-related companies. Our team has undertaken the task to help FishEye conduct a visual analytics study and exploration with the aim to identify fishing business anomalies that could indicate a company is involved in IUU.
